Complete
========
x Thu Feb  9 11:44:27 AKST 2012 - Now with VMware ESXi 5, it is possible to perform an 
automated installation to USB storage.  Simply specify usb-storage as part of the install 
command in an automated install script.

For example:
  install --firstdisk=usb-storage --overwritevmfs

Create ESXi 5.0 usb boot stick with access to local drives and raid?

vcritical.com/


